 memory storage applications and is likely to\nelucidate a new route to tune useful magnetic properties. Moreover, this method\nis much more convenient than hetero-structure and other cumbersome techniques.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Dec 2022 08:42:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-02"}
